OL,3,CDeborah James' mum hails bowel cancer
OL,4,Cscreening age extension
OL,6,FSpeaking to The Sun, Ms. James added:
OL,7,F"Deborah will be up there grinning
OL,8,Ffrom ear to ear, jumping for joy.
OL,10,F"But I know she would want to urge
OL,11,Fanyone who gets a screening invite to
OL,12,Ftake the test.
OL,14,F"She was all too aware that many
OL,15,Fpeople ignore the invite and put off
OL,16,Ftheir test, a decision that can prove
OL,17,Ffatal."
