OL,3,CDeborah James' mum hails bowel cancer
OL,4,Cscreening age extension
OL,6,FThose aged 50 and 52 will receive kits
OL,7,Fby the end of March, and people aged
OL,8,F51 and 53 will be posted a kit after
OL,9,Ftheir next birthday.
OL,11,FThe faecal immunochemical test (FIT)
OL,12,Fchecks for blood in a stool sample,
OL,13,Fwith people collecting their own
OL,14,Fsample at home before posting it back
OL,15,Fto NHS labs in a prepaid return
OL,16,Fenvelope.
OL,18,FResults are then sent out to people,
OL,19,Falong with any information about
OL,20,Ffurther tests, if required.
