OL,4,Cscreening age extension
OL,6,FFigures show that fewer than 60% of 54
OL,7,Fto 57-year-olds take up the test,
OL,8,Fcompared with more than 70% of those
OL,9,Faged 60 to 74.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FPeople are much more likely to survive
OL,17,Fbowel cancer or have successful
OL,18,Ftreatment if the disease is caught
OL,19,Fbefore it has spread.
