OL,3,CDeborah James' mum hails bowel cancer
OL,4,Cscreening age extension
OL,6,FSteve Russell, national director for
OL,7,Fvaccinations and screening at NHS
OL,8,FEngland, said: "While taking a test
OL,9,Ffor bowel cancer may be the last thing
OL,10,Fyou're thinking about as you enter the
OL,11,Fnew year, it could save your life".
OL,13,FBowel cancer is one of the most common
OL,14,Fcancers affecting people in the UK,
OL,15,Fwith more than 44,000 new cases every
OL,16,Fyear.
