OL,3,CDeborah James' mum hails bowel cancer
OL,4,Cscreening age extension
OL,6,FAnyone with symptoms of bowel cancer
OL,7,Fis urged to contact their GP and not
OL,8,Fwait for a test.
OL,10,FSigns include stomach pain lasting
OL,11,Fthree weeks or more, blood in stools,
OL,12,Fdiarrhoea or constipation for no
OL,13,Fobvious reason lasting three weeks or
OL,14,Fmore, a feeling of not having emptied
OL,15,Fthe bowels after going to the toilet,
OL,16,Fbottom pain and loose, pale or greasy
OL,17,Fstools.
